data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence is nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, offering both serenity and space for your family. The interior boasts a fully finished English basement, providing additional living and entertainment space for all your needs. Step into a home where every detail has been carefully considered and updated. Upgraded, neutral flooring that adds both style and durability in the main living spaces. The cohesive design flows seamlessly from room to room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. Fresh, modern paint that complements the abundance of natural light flowing through the windows. The spacious kitchen is equipped with brand-new appliances, solid surface counters, 42" cabinets and tile backsplash. This updated kitchen is perfect for creating culinary masterpieces for family and friends. The 5 well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and privacy. The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom with double vanity and separate shower and spacious walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are versatile and can be adapted to suit your lifestyle. Venture outside to your own private oasis - a beautiful pool awaits, surrounded by a meticulously landscaped yard and deck off the kitchen, creating a perfect setting for outdoor gatherings and summer fun. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.
